**Send Email Tab**  
The Send Email tab in the CRM is used to log every email you send to a lead from your connected email account.

Whenever you send an email to a lead, you must fill out this form to properly track communication and ensure follow-ups are scheduled.

**✉️To access the Send Email tab::**

Open the company card of the lead you emailed.  
Go to the “Send Email” tab in the top menu.,  
In the top right corner of this tab, click the downward arrow (▾) to expand and open the Send Email Form.  
**✅ Required Fields to Complete**

**LG Manager –** This field is filled automatically with your name as the lead generation manager.

**Lead Accounts –** Select the email account you used to send the message.

**Type Email –** Select “General” (used for most communication).

**Send Date –** Enter the exact date when the email was sent.

**Follow-Up Date –** Choose a follow-up date, typically 1 week after the send date, to ensure the lead is contacted again if needed.